    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Dimensions of original manuscript:  275 x 204 (190 x 132) mm. bound to 288 x 224 mm.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Title supplied by cataloger.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Decoration:  2 full-page color illustrations in gouache and ink of constellation maps (p. 112-113); 43 smaller illustrations of constellations  in gouache and ink with gold bezants for stars (p. 117-144); panel headpiece in interlaced red and green penwork and full border of gold bezants flourished in colored ink (p. 1); numerous full-page diagrams and tables in red and brown ink; Gothic penwork infilling frames on some tables (p. 196-211); headings in red or green ink.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Script:  Written in Sephardic cursive script by multiple hands, one perhaps of a scribe named Moshe (p. 2); headings written in square script.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Layout:  Text written in 2 columns of 37 lines; some leaves ruled in faint ink.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Foliation:  Parchment, iv (modern paper) + 114 + iv (modern paper; [1-228]; modern pagination in pencil, upper outer corners.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Origin:  Written in Catalonia, ca. 1361.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1=" " ind2=" " tag="500">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Binding:  Modern blind-stamped morocco, with 2 sets of clasps and catches.</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="505">
  <marc:subfield code="a">4. p.69-86:  [Mishpeṭe ha-mazalot (Book of the judgments of the zodiacal signs) / Abraham ben Meïr Ibn Ezra]</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="505">
  <marc:subfield code="a">3. p.61-68:  [Sefer ha-mivḥarim (Book of elections) / Abraham ben Meïr Ibn Ezra]</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="505">
  <marc:subfield code="a">2. p.25-60:  [Reshit ḥokhmah (Beginning of wisdom) / Abraham ben Meïr Ibn Ezra]</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="505">
  <marc:subfield code="a">1. p.1-23:  [Treatise on calendar and leap years / Jacob ben David ben Yom Tov]</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="0" ind2=" " tag="505">
